{"tid":2421512,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港府突然宣布上調股票印花稅30%    恆生指數崩跌逾千點","createTime":"2021-02-24T14:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T04:12:23.000Z","uid":79563,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"c357e640699b395b99b90412e40a998fa49024bc","tid":2421512,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:10:20.000Z","msg":"周三 (24 日) 香港財政司司長陳茂波於財政預算案中公布，將提高股票印花稅，買賣雙方上調 30%，由買賣雙方各支付 0.1% 的印花稅，提高至 0.13%。港股聞訊崩跌，午盤後恆生指數重挫逾 1000 點，恆生科技指數大跌約 6%，南向資金亦瘋狂賣出近 150 億港元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OCahTu8jMX2P4df6A0U.fg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQyOS43NDcyOTI0MTg3NzI2/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/n4fds8WhOTRqOLxWh2puig--~B/aD0yNDg7dz01NTQ7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/94595ce196e0563c93c34f4f8acf1f64\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FOCahTu8jMX2P4df6A0U.fg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQyOS43NDcyOTI0MTg3NzI2%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fn4fds8WhOTRqOLxWh2puig--~B%2FaD0yNDg7dz01NTQ7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fcnyes_hk_559%2F94595ce196e0563c93c34f4f8acf1f64&h=82b34c9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n針對上調股票印花稅港交所首當其衝，其發言人回應稱，對港府提高股票交易印花稅的決定感到失望，但明白該稅項是政府收入的重要來源。<br />\n<br />\n周三香港財政司司長陳茂波表示，充分考慮對證券市場和國際競爭力的影響後，決定提交法案調整股票印花稅稅率，由目前買賣雙方依交易金額支付 0.1%，提高至 0.13%。<br />\n<br />\n2020 財政年度，香港的印花稅佔政府收入大約一成，其中又有約一半來自股票交易印花稅。去年，證券市場的平均每日成交額達 1290 億港元，年增率逾 48%。<br />\n<br />\n在全球主要股市中，並非所有政府都徵收股票印花稅，香港增加股票印花稅後，稅率將較中國 A 股擴大差距，在全球僅次於英國。<br />\n<br />\n目前香港股票印花稅為帳上每年帶來 500 億港元稅收，港府消息人士透露，股票印花稅將由今年 8 月 1 日起上調，預計為下一個財政年度額外增加 80 億港元收入。<br />\n<br />\n香港基金經理表示，從業以來都不曾碰到過印花稅調整。這次突發事件，估計對港股會有衝擊，但難以預料會有衝擊會多大。"},{"pid":"8b2d0e35326d2640af701949046bf5638612ecf1","tid":2421512,"uid":51920,"like":13,"dislike":8,"score":5,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:11:36.000Z","msg":"1000萬先收多你3千蚊<br />\n大戶食個飯都唔止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a16fdaa6672068295a4c483473bc20df5c0e4fd","tid":2421512,"uid":347528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:12:42.000Z","msg":"抄底啦"},{"pid":"e09f48e9441c8f45b251b77e0e7d5bb0607f2d7b","tid":2421512,"uid":435,"like":24,"dislike":2,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"8b2d0e35326d2640af701949046bf5638612ecf1","tid":2421512,"uid":51920,"like":13,"dislike":8,"score":5,"citedBy":11,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:11:36.000Z","msg":"1000萬先收多你3千蚊<br />\n大戶食個飯都唔止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:15:01.000Z","msg":"班day trader唔係咁睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本來已經貴仲要加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceceae8f96425b97d70f32d6ce53ba49476be007","tid":2421512,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:15:23.000Z","msg":"咁少怕咩"},{"pid":"9c7acfc7feebaa8008e2ab282f766c9b88f4e628","tid":2421512,"uid":60000,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c357e640699b395b99b90412e40a998fa49024bc","tid":2421512,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T14:10:20.000Z","msg":"周三 (24 日) 香港財政司司長陳茂波於財政預算案中公布，將提高股票印花稅，買賣雙方上調 30%，由買賣雙方各支付 0.1% 的印花稅，提高至 0.13%。港股聞訊崩跌，午盤後恆生指數重挫逾 1000 點，恆生科技指數大跌約 6%，南向資金亦瘋狂賣出近 150 億港元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/OCahTu8jMX2P4df6A0U.fg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQyOS43NDcyOTI0MTg3NzI2/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/n4fds8WhOTRqOLxWh2puig--~B/aD0yNDg7dz01NTQ7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/94595ce196e0563c93c34f4f8acf1f64\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FOCahTu8jMX2P4df6A0U.fg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTQyOS43NDcyOTI0MTg3NzI2%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fn4fds8WhOTRqOLxWh2puig--~B%2FaD0yNDg7dz01NTQ7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2F